metadata.name: Shift AI
metadata.description: Shift AI is a next-generation portfolio management platform built on the Solana blockchain. It enables users to create and manage cryptocurrency portfolios with ease, supporting assets like BTC, ETH, SOL, SUI, XRP, and more. By leveraging Solana’s speed and scalability, along with bridging technology, Wormhole, and wrapped assets, Shift AI offers seamless and efficient portfolio customization through a simple, intuitive interface. Designed for flexibility, it adapts to the evolving demands of the digital asset market. Shift AI will be open source, with the code available on GitHub, allowing developers to deploy and contribute to the platform’s growth.
